Back To School Message From Superintendent Goncalves - Dear Bloomfield District Staff:

As I embark on my 43rd year in the district and my 7th year as your Superintendent of Schools, I am pleased to welcome you to the 2019-2020 school year! I want to thank our Board of Education members for their continuous support, our 12-month administrators and staff, as well as our 10-month staff members who worked over this summer and participated in important planning sessions in order to ensure an exciting start of the school year. http://edne.tw/n583806
